{"tid":1058682,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"啲人成日問點解任天堂唔同另兩家鬥機能，計我話佢特登唔鬥先至醒目啊。","createTime":"2019-03-12T16:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T21:33:53.000Z","uid":238189,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7e75f8fea6fb512030edc753751eb617d96cfea7","tid":1058682,"uid":238189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"Sony同Microsoft都有一系列電子產業，手機電腦賣到成行成市，有大把資源同人力可以回饋於遊戲部門上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反任天堂雖然都有長年累積落黎嘅經驗同$，但始終只係一間單純嘅遊戲公司，偶爾搞下周邊合作咁樣(起緊主題公園)。<br />\n如果夾硬同另兩家爭崩頭，使太多資源投放落各種產業上，難保唔會潑水難收，步當年Sega嘅後塵，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時就幾多好遊戲同IP都救唔到公司。<br />\n所以你見點解自N64同NGC銷量不佳之後(唔算衰但都唔算好)，從Wii開始，任天堂都係行機能不足，創意搭夠嘅路線(不過WiiU創意同機能都不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。夾硬鬥機能對大家都冇好處。<br />\n利申我玩遊戲而唔係玩平臺，冇話對邊一家特別傾側，純粹個人睇法，打手退散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"89efb714433e461740237c7f24ffedf63f48ef16","tid":1058682,"uid":16945,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"好似xbox咁部幾勁都冇用，而家連鬼佬都唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcd343bf2b058a8f65d7b8df7faa077e51c9acf","tid":1058682,"uid":239954,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcdd83175a53bc090a5f0cfd4c1a24ba1cb2133e","tid":1058682,"uid":238189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcd343bf2b058a8f65d7b8df7faa077e51c9acf","tid":1058682,"uid":239954,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"你個名，難分曲與直<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835c0b4ce2ee66b1da8f7f13eb7d4ba4f4b8c2bd","tid":1058682,"uid":19365,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:22:25.000Z","msg":"你估D人成日問機能